ocument review assurance; Elevated trust is mandatory for this document review request.; aliases=['high assurance for document review']\n\nARTIFACT CONTRACTS\n- v07-p01-json: document review machine-readable JSON; Return the final document review result as JSON.; aliases=['document review json output']\n- v07-p01-signed-pdf: document review signed PDF; Return the final document review result as a signed PDF.; aliases=['signed document review document']\n\nAGENTS\n- v07-p01-preparer: document review source preparer\n- v07-p01-verifier: document review source verifier\n- v07-p01-primary: primary document review publisher\n- v07-p01-backup: backup document review publisher\n\nREQUEST\nFor this document review job, gather and check the material, then retain the brief for the long term with normal document review assurance as document review JSON output."
